thcare, interactive marketing and publishing.'),(13226,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_paragraph','field_533c6d9feba92'),(13227,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_name','Philip Dur'),(13228,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13229,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_position','Co-Chair Investor Growth Capital'),(13230,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13231,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_bio','Philip Dur has been involved in venture capital and private equity since 1995 and joined Investor Growth Capital’s technology investment team in 2004. He works out of IGC\'s Menlo Park office and focuses on investments in software and technology-enabled services businesses.'),(13232,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_0_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13233,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_name','Richard Harroch'),(13234,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13235,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_position','Co-Chair Vantage Point Capital Partners'),(13236,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13237,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','Richard Harroch joined VantagePoint in 2003 from Orrick, Herrington & Sutcliffe LLP, bringing with him an extensive body of transactional and business expertise. He is a successful entrepreneur, founder and Chairman of two companies: LawCommerce.com (sold to LexisNexis) and Allbusiness.com (sold to Dun and Bradstreet.)'),(13238,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_1_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13239,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_name','Michael Barber'),(13240,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13241,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_position','Vice President, healthymagination GE Corporate'),(13242,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13243,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_bio','Michael Barber is a GE Officer and the VP of GE’s business strategy on global health for the corporation. The healthymagination charter is to improve the quality of care by 15% or more, to reduce the cost of procedures and processes through the appropriate use of GE technologies and services by 15% and to increase the access to essential technologies and services essential to health by 15%.'),(13244,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_2_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13245,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_name','Kevin Brown'),(13246,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13247,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_position','General Partner Reed Elsevier Ventures'),(13248,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13249,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_bio','Kevin Brown has been involved in early stage technology & venture capital since the late nineties, first as an entrepreneur & then as an investor. He was a founding partner of Reed Elsevier Ventures in 2000 & has specialised in digital media, Internet and large scale data & technology investments since then.'),(13250,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_3_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13251,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_name','Richard H. Carmona, MD, MPH'),(13252,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13253,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_position','FACS 17th Surgeon General of the United States (2002-2006)'),(13254,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13255,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_bio','In 2002, Dr. Carmona was nominated by the president and unanimously confirmed by the United States Senate to become the 17th Surgeon General of the United States. He is president of the non-profit Canyon Ranch Institute and Distinguished Professor at the Zuckerman College of Public Health at the University of Arizona.'),(13256,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_4_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13257,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_name','Paul T. Sheils'),(13258,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13259,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_position','Managing Director Ansley Capital Group'),(13260,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13261,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_bio','Prior to joining The Ansley Capital Group, Paul Sheils was President & CEO of DocSite, LLC, an award-winning healthcare quality improvement and performance management company. He was also Founder and Managing Partner of Silverado Health Partners, LLC, a digital health management consulting firm, whose clients included GE Healthcare, J&J, UnitedHealth Group, and Hearst Digital Media.'),(13262,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_5_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13263,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_name','Jim Warner'),(13264,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_name','field_533c6dd3eba9e'),(13265,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_position',''),(13266,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_position','field_533c6ddeeba9f'),(13267,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_bio','Jim Warner has a long and successful career as a leader in digital marketing and media. Most recently, he was at Avenue A|Razorfish and its parent company, aQuantive, where he advised a number of Fortune 500 companies including Capital One, Verizon and Starwood Hotels, on digital marketing, advertising and web strategy.'),(13268,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets_6_bio','field_533c6de5ebaa0'),(13269,481,'about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets','7'),(13270,481,'_about_us_page_content_1_directors_buckets','field_533c6dbaeba9d'),(13271,481,'about_us_page_content_2_headline','Medical Advisory Board'),(13272,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_headline','field_533c6ffafd655'),(13273,481,'about_us_page_content_2_paragraph','The Healthline Medical Advisory Board is comprised of nationally and internationally recognized medical experts who serve to better the Healthline user experience by evaluating our website content, making recommendations on the vision and direction of the site, and providing input into Healthline\'s Medically Guided Search components, including its taxonomy, navigation and other features. The board also interfaces with customers and partners that use or offer the Healthline search experience.'),(13274,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_paragraph','field_533c6ffafd656'),(13275,481,'about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_name','Paul Auerbach, MD, MS, FACEP'),(13276,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_name','field_533c6ffafd658'),(13277,481,'about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_position','Chair, Medical Advisory Board'),(13278,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_position','field_533c6ffafd659'),(13279,481,'about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_bio','Dr. Auerbach is the Redlich Family Professor of Surgery in the Division of Emergency Medicine at Stanford University. He is internationally recognized as a leading authority on emergency medicine, wilderness medicine and outdoor health and safety.'),(13280,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_0_bio','field_533c6ffafd65a'),(13281,481,'about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_1_name','Colleen Conway-Welch, PhD, RN, FAAN'),(13282,481,'_about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_1_name','field_533c6ffafd658'),(13283,481,'about_us_page_content_2_advisory_buckets_1_position','Medical Advisory Board Member'),(13284,481,'_about_us_page_cont